'''Lesser Demons''' are [[Monster|monsters]] with a [[combat level]] of 79. They are especially weak to the [[Silverlight]] sword.

Note: [[Silverlight]] has to be wielded while making the initial attack (''first hit''), otherwise the special ability will not activate.

== Locations ==
*South of [[Demonic Ruins]]
*Inside [[Karamja Volcano]] and in [[Crandor]]
*Guarding the ladder down to the [[King black dragon]] lair
*Guarding the [[Muddy chest|Muddy Key Chest]] in the [[Lava Maze]]
*[[Melzar's Maze]] basement 
*[[Legends caverns]]
*[[Taverley dungeon]]
*[[Temple of Ikov]]
*In the top floor of the [[Wizards' Tower]], in the jail cell ('''Note''': ''This lesser demon can only be killed with [[ranged]] or [[magic]]'')

